## Requirements
- OpenGL 3.3
- GLEW
- GLFW
- GLM
- GLU
- stb_image

## Program Usage
execute this from the main folder where Makefile is present.
To compile and execute calculator
```
make run
```

Use mouse curser to rotate camera.

Use M to change mapping.
Use T to change texture.
Use S to speed up the models.
Use D to slow down the models.

Use 1, 2, 3, 4 keys to select objects in the scene.

After selecting model:
Use L to on and off the light.
Use R to start and stop vertical rotation of each model.

## Executables
Executables will be created in bin folder.
